OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FAlmost half of London bus drivers
OL,7,Frecently surveyed have revealed
OL,8,Fthey've nearly had an accident due to
OL,9,Fa lack of rest between shifts,
OL,10,Fscheduling and alleged forced overtime.
OL,12,FFigures from Unite the Union
OL,13,Fhighlighted the reality of bus drivers
OL,14,Fwho regularly experience all of these
OL,15,Fproblems when working.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FThe survey of more than 2,000
OL,7,Fresponses by the union also found over
OL,8,Fa third of drivers have experienced
OL,9,Fsleepiness while driving two or three
OL,10,Ftimes a week, while nearly a quarter
OL,11,Fhad this happen once a week.
OL,13,FUnite is now urging Transport for
OL,14,FLondon (TfL) to address working
OL,15,Fconditions and stop putting drivers
OL,16,Fand the public in danger.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
