OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FITV News London has previously
OL,7,Finvestigated the reality of being a
OL,8,Fbus driver in the capital, which
OL,9,Funcovered claims that long hours,
OL,10,Fexhausting schedules and inadequate
OL,11,Frest are leading to widespread fatigue.
OL,13,FOne current driver who has previously
OL,14,Fspoken to ITV News London said drivers
OL,15,F"feel ignored" by TFL and their
OL,16,Foperators.
OL,18,FThey also said, as well as not taking
OL,19,Fbreaks, there's a lack of toilets
OL,20,Fwhich also pose a problem for many
OL,21,Fdrivers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FBus drivers also said extreme fatigue
OL,7,Fwas causing them concentration issues
OL,8,Fas well as health issues including
OL,9,Fchronic pain, cardiovascular problems
OL,10,Fand stress and anxiety.
OL,12,FUnite's poll found 83 per cent of bus
OL,13,Fdrivers are scared to tell their
OL,14,Femployers that they are fatigued out
OL,15,Fof fear they will be penalised, such
OL,16,Fas discipline, loss of earnings, or
OL,17,Floss of rest day working.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FUnite the Union want TfL, which
OL,7,Fsubcontracts out bus work to private
OL,8,Fcompanies, and the employers to
OL,9,Fintroduce a range of measures to
OL,10,Fensure bus drivers are properly looked
OL,11,Fafter.
OL,13,FTheir campaign 'Fight Fatigue Now'
OL,14,Faims to reduce fatigue by establishing
OL,15,Fconsistency across scheduling and
OL,16,Frosters and improve rest, toilet and
OL,17,Fwelfare facilities.
OL,19,FThe campaign also outlines the need
OL,20,Ffor better fatigue management.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fhas condemed the survey findings,
OL,8,Fdetailing how poor driver conditions
OL,9,Fare a risk to not only themselves but
OL,10,Falso the public.
OL,12,FShe said: "The results of Unite's
OL,13,Fsurvey are damning ` the time between
OL,14,Frests, poor scheduling, not enough
OL,15,Ftime between shifts and forced
OL,16,Fovertime is putting both bus drivers
OL,17,Fand the public in danger.
OL,19,F"This is a completely unacceptable
OL,20,Fsituation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,F"No worker should be overworked to the
OL,7,Fpoint where they are so fatigued they
OL,8,Fare falling asleep at the wheel and
OL,9,Frisking their lives while doing their
OL,10,Fjob.
OL,12,F"It is clear that TfL and bus
OL,13,Foperators are not treating the fatigue
OL,14,Fcrisis with the seriousness it
OL,15,Fdeserves and Unite will fight tooth
OL,16,Fand nail to ensure this changes."
OL,26,@xD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
