OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,FLorna Murphy, TfL's Director of Buses,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Bus drivers play a vital role
OL,8,Fin keeping London moving, and the
OL,9,Fwelfare of both our drivers and
OL,10,Fcustomers is paramount.
OL,12,F"Working closely with Unite, bus
OL,13,Foperators and drivers, we set and
OL,14,Fenforce high standards so that drivers
OL,15,Fare supported by safe vehicles, fair
OL,16,Fwork schedules and the facilities they
OL,17,Fneed to do their jobs effectively.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,F"We have longstanding programmes in
OL,7,Fplace covering education, health and
OL,8,Fwellbeing, rest facilities, workplace
OL,9,Fculture and clear welfare policies,
OL,10,Fwith a strong focus on understanding
OL,11,Fand tackling fatigue. This includes
OL,12,Fimproving how we gather and analyse
OL,13,Fdata on when fatigue occurs, alongside
OL,14,Fthe recent introduction of
OL,15,Ffatiguedetection technology, so the
OL,16,Fright, evidencebased interventions
OL,17,Fcan be put in place.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
