OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776435067
OL,3,CCalls for better bus driver conditions
OL,4,Cas extreme fatigue causes safety fears
OL,6,F"We have not seen Unite's survey, but
OL,7,Fwe welcome all input on fatigue and
OL,8,Fwill continue working with Unite to
OL,9,Faddress it.
OL,11,F"Any concerns raised by drivers are
OL,12,Falways taken seriously and fully
OL,13,Finvestigated, and operators should
OL,14,Fnever take action against anyone
OL,15,Fraising welfare or safety issues."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
